product.name: Are You Kidding Bare - Coma Inducer® Oversized Comforter - Antarctica Grey
product.shortDescription: Inspired by untamed coziness that is so soft  and plush that it begs the question "Are You Kidding?" Seriously... you  wrap yourself up and you know a comfort level this high makes you think  it can't be real. It must be a dream.
product.description:
Inspired by untamed coziness that is so soft  and plush that it begs the question "Are You Kidding?" Seriously... you  wrap yourself up and you know a comfort level this high makes you think  it can't be real. It must be a dream. No bedding can feel this good,  right? Or can it? With long silk-like, luxurious fibers that seemingly  engulf your skin in a cradle of comfort, you just know that you've found  the very best with "Are You Kidding®" Comforters. This particular Are  You Kidding® bedding is turbocharged with comfort by the reverse side  being made with Byourbed's luxury Bare Bottom® material. A fabric that  can only be explained by imagining yourself bundled in a stick of  creamy, cozy soft butter. This insanely cozy combination of plush  creates our most versatile Coma Inducer® - the aptly named Are You Kidding Bare. 


Experience ultimate sleeping comfort with the Are You Kidding Bare Coma Inducer Antarctica Grey Oversized Comforter. This warm, thick comforter features a plush fabric face and a reverse side made of exclusive, silky-soft Bare Bottom microfiber material infused with spandex. The 280 GSM down alternative microfiber fill provides an extra layer of softness and warmth. Box-stitched to keep the fill evenly distributed, this oversized comforter is easy to care for and machine washable. Available in Twin XL, Full XL, Queen XL, or King XL sizes so you can choose the perfect plush comforter for your cozy bedding set. Plus, the easy to match color of this grey oversized comforter make it easy to match your bedding essentials with your bedroom decor!


Features:

  • Includes 1 comforter (Shams Sold Separate)
  • Face made of warm, cozy plush fabric
  • Reverse side made of Bare Bottom (microfiber infused with spandex)
  • 280 GSM down alternative microfiber fill
  • Box stitched to keep fill evenly distributed
  • Warm, thick, and oversized
  • Soft and stretchy material
  • Care Instructions: Machine Washable - Gentle Cycle / Cold Wash

Dimensions:

  • Twin XL: 68 inches wide x 90 inches long
  • Full: 88 inches wide x 90 inches long
  • Queen: 94 inches wide x 98 inches long
  • King: 112 inches wide x 98 inches long

questions.text: What are the dimensions for the oversized king size? It only states the same dimensions for all sizes

answers.text: King: 112 inches wide x 98 inches long

questions.text: will the twin xl fit a full size bed

answers.text: The Twin XL would be too narrow for a Full size bed. We would recommend choosing the Queen option if the Full size is not available.

questions.text: Do this comforter come in purple?

answers.text: This particular style of comforter does not come in a purple color unfortunately.

questions.text: What is your favorite feature of this product?

answers.text: Beautiful and my building is 13B and apt. 1
I already own this product and I love it!

questions.text: please answer the question laundering this large comforter, I have a king comforter and, also a. King River cover. Both are generous in size, but neither fit in my washer comfortably to wash and dry them in machines.  A local cleaners  will.was them for $25.00 each as of 3.5 years ago. I will not pay that much when frequent washes are necessary.  BTW, THE duvet also has to.be ironed.......so it's VERY IMPORTANT. please ask the manufacturers suggestion on laundering this lovely but huge..comforter. Thank you. There have to.be others who really need to know this who have.possibly not considered  they would have to literally cram it into washer and have it come out also looking and staying very wrinkled.

answers.text: Take to laundry Matt use the xl washer maybe $5 to wash but I won’t put in my washer again and mine is a queen size.

questions.text: What is the best way to wash and dry this ?
Does this come in any other color?

answers.text: Yes, this item is also currently available in Nightfall Navy, Charcoal Gray, and Farmhouse White. Please search Overstock for "Are You Kidding Bare - Coma Inducer Oversized Comforter" to find all available colors of this bedding.

questions.text: what is the weight of the queen comforter?

answers.text: The Twin XL Comforter weighs about 8 lbs, the Queen about 11lbs, and the King about 13 lbs.

questions.text: Is this the same thing as a down comforter?

answers.text: This comforter has a 280 GSM Down Alternative Microfiber Fill, which is not the same as standard Down.

questions.text: Do you have pillow cases available?

answers.text: Yes, the matching pillow shams are available for purchase. They can be located on Overstock by searching "36714413".
